==Indonesian==
===Etymology===
Derived from root [[ada]]
===Verb===
====[[Intransitive]] [[active voice|Active]]====
'''berada'''
#to [[happen]] to be at/in
#to be [[located]] at/in
#* [[Rumah]] [[saya]] '''berada''' [[pantai]] [[selatan]].
#* My house is located on the south coast.

